metadata.name: Peper
metadata.description: "Peper Rescue Club" consist of 5555 unique "Peper" to the rescue NFT collection which focuses on our best friend. "Peper" is a rescued pet and a sign for a true friendship. We have brought "Peper" as we see him in our imagination each one is unique and special on its on way. A part of every "Peper Rescue Club" NFT sale will be donated to save an another pet life around the world. Your own unique "Peper" will brighten up your day. Enjoy your new best friend in the Metaverse.
